About this item    HANDCRAFTED & HIGH QUALITY: CT copper range hoods are constructed using solid, genuine 16 gauge copper that ensures durability and longevity. 9 color options allow it to complement both farmhouse-style and modern style kitchen decor. Hand-hammered individually by professionals, this copper range hood features handcrafted unique textures, making it a decorative focal point of the kitchen.    POWERFUL HOOD INSERT: The blower can reach 610(30"/36")/960CFM(42"/48") at its maximum suction.For a 30"/36" hood, Its fan can operate at 4 speeds in total, with the other three yielding 280,390, and 520CFM. For the 42"/48" copper kitchen hood, the other three-speed is 385/490/615CFM. The whole operation is quiet even at the highest speed. The LED lights provide illumination for the cook-top area at night.    SIMPLE CLEANING & MAINTENANCE: The clear lacquer coating on copper hoods help prevent corrosion, so they won't rust like standard copper hoods. Stainless steel baffle filters are included to trap grease and oil. The reusable filters can be easily removed and cleaned in the dishwasher.    SAFETY & WARRANTY: The hood vent is UL listed and ETL approved for your safety and protection. An industry-leading two-year parts warranty and lifetime hood cover warranty gives you peace of mind. A Shop drawing will be sent to you once an order is placed.    NOTE: If you want to get an idea of copper patina and texture, search B07VTNGT64 to get copper sample packs. Size customization is available, please contact us to get a quote. Since our products are handmade from copper, small differences in patina and texture can occur. We do not consider product variances as defects.

About this item    Powerful But Quiet: The main body of our built-in range hood is made of stainless steel, with ETL certification, providing high strength and durability. It is rust-proof and corrosion-proof for easy cleaning. The galvanized motor offers powerful suction with a maximum of 800CFM speed. It can easily and effectively take away large amounts of smoke and oil grease from the air in your kitchen. Meanwhile, the noise level at the highest speed is low at 62dB, bringing you a quiet cooking zone.    Easy-Operating Panel: This insert vent hood adopts push-button control, which can be used easily via simply selecting the mode you need. It has a 3-speed adjustment, which allows you freely switch between low, medium, and high fan speeds according to different cooking requirements. A light button can conveniently turn on or off the two equipped LED lights.    Superior Filtration: Our range vent hood contains double-layer filtration. The 2 detachable stainless steel filters can effectively block cooking grease and oil. Its easy-to-clean design allows you to reuse it forever just by putting it in the dishwasher. The charcoal filter, made from high-quality activated carbon, can block harmful particulates and absorb smoke in the air, bringing the fresh air to you and your family.    Humanized Design: With the built-in design, our range hood is easy to install and saves your kitchen space. It includes two 3W LED lamps with warm light, which are bright but not dazzling, and energy-saving. Besides, there is a plastic box in the front of the motor for collecting excess oil.    Ducted/Ductless Convertible: Our insert kitchen hood is suitable for ducted and ductless kitchens. With an extra 59.1inch / 1.5m detachable duct, fully-filtered fresh air can be circulated indoors or discharged outdoors.
